@startuml Concept Diagram - ECS Architecture

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Game Engine - Concept Architecture (ECS Pattern)

package "Concept Layer" {
    rectangle "World\n(Điều phối)" as WorldConcept #LightBlue
    rectangle "System\n(Xử lý Logic)" as SystemConcept #LightGreen
    rectangle "Entity\n(Container)" as EntityConcept #LightYellow
    rectangle "Component\n(Chức năng)" as ComponentConcept #LightCoral
}

' Concept relationships
WorldConcept --> SystemConcept : "quản lý\n(manages)"
SystemConcept --> EntityConcept : "xử lý\n(processes)"
EntityConcept --> ComponentConcept : "chứa\n(contains)"
ComponentConcept --> SystemConcept : "đăng ký\n(registers)"

note top of WorldConcept
  **World - Điều phối viên**
  - Quản lý game loop
  - Điều phối tất cả systems
  - Update/Render cycle
end note

note right of SystemConcept
  **System - Xử lý logic**
  - Xử lý entities/components
  - Logic nghiệp vụ chuyên biệt
  - Update mỗi frame
end note

note bottom of EntityConcept
  **Entity - Container**
  - Chứa các components
  - Quản lý lifecycle
  - Trạng thái active/inactive
end note

note left of ComponentConcept
  **Component - Chức năng**
  - Mở rộng entity
  - Đăng ký với systems
  - Lifecycle hooks
end note

@enduml


